        <updateDate>2019-09-04T20:22:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Continuation of Useful Resources to States Act or COURTS Act</b></p> <p>This bill extends and otherwise revises funding for programs related to child welfare. Specifically, the bill extends through FY2022 funding for&nbsp;(1) the Promoting Safe and Stable Families Program, and (2) the grant program for improving courts' handling of foster-care and adoption proceedings.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
